README

1.
 Add screenshot.mm, ASScreenRecorder.h, ASScreenRecorder.m to "Classes Folder"

2.
 Go to Project Navigator>Targets>Link Binary With Libraries and add AssetLibrary.framework

3.
 In Project Navigator>Targets>Compile Sources, add all *.m and *.mm files we added if they are not there.

4.
 Add strings from appPermissions.txt to Info.plist file source code (right click file and select Open As>Source Code)

5.
 screenshot.cs is a file for Unity.